Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.62,0:00:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好像不来电耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.95,0:00:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.95,0:00:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那黑泽呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.79,0:00:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.45,0:00:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.12,0:00:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是要外国人啊\N对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.45,0:00:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要求这么高啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.95,0:00:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我不会英文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.12,0:00:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.12,0:00:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着是1007室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.62,0:00:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人在等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.79,0:00:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.12,0:01:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.12,0:01:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲击的解禁\N黑人跟美熟女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.45,0:01:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢白色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.12,0:01:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人说的话不一定是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.29,0:01:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不讲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.29,0:01:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没人知道我在做这一行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.79,0:01:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以所见的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.29,0:01:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不一定是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.95,0:01:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有一件一定是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.79,0:02:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我不懂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.29,0:02:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等好久唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.79,0:02:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.29,0:02:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.45,0:02:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.95,0:04:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.12,0:04:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别坐在这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.12,0:04:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.45,0:07:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.79,0:07:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来 坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.29,0:07:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.12,0:07:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.29,0:07:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.79,0:08:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.12,0:08:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在干什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.95,0:08:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.95,0:11:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.12,0:11:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你几岁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.12,0:11:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,27岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.95,0:12:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该辞掉这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.29,0:12:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想未来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.12,0:12:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也常被问还不结婚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.12,0:12:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我该走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.79,0:12:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在结束了 我要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.95,0:13:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是客人太无聊的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.79,0:13:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 应该幻象想些更好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.45,0:15:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.79,0:15:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.29,0:15:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.79,0:15:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.12,0:15:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.62,0:16:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有付钱吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.45,0:16:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.95,0:16:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.29,0:16:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在等你唷 快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.12,0:16:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要帮忙吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.45,0:17:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有藏吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.62,0:17:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.12,0:17:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.45,0:18:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.29,0:18:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快脱掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.29,0:18:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.79,0:18:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.29,0:18:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像没东西 不过...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.12,0:19:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再试看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.29,0:19:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.45,0:19:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.12,0:19:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有东西吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.62,0:19:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再摸看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.12,0:19:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你闻看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.12,0:19:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.12,0:20:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有东西吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.29,0:20:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.62,0:20:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像投有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.79,0:20:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只好用别的方法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.12,0:20:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带她过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.12,0:22:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.95,0:23:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.29,0:23:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.12,0:25:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.29,0:25:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:21.62,0:25:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:04.95,0:26:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:21.12,0:27:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:02.12,0:30:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:22.29,0:33:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人 要结帐吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:27.79,0:33:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,928元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:42.62,0:33:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚好 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:34.79,0:35:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢白花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:38.29,0:35:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白色就是我的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:42.62,0:35:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,床好软
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:45.79,0:35:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以忘记讨厌的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:50.29,0:35:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的空间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:55.29,0:35:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人可以伤害我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:06.79,0:40:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:30.62,0:40:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:59.29,0:42:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:04.45,0:42:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:20.45,0:42:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好饿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:25.29,0:42:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有东西吃吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:55.62,0:46:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:16.29,0:47:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:22.62,0:47:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:05.12,0:48:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:10.45,0:50:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以看吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:57.29,0:50:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:04.12,0:51:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以舔吗？\N好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:23.95,0:52:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:42.12,0:55:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:15.29,0:56:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:30.12,1:01:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:22.45,1:04:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又做梦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:26.29,1:04:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是太累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:19.12,1:07:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总有一天会遇到王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:23.29,1:07:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在白色的房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:27.79,1:07:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是普通的OL遇不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:33.62,1:07:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才边当OL
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:36.95,1:07:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,边赚钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:42.29,1:07:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点来 我的白马王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:46.95,1:07:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在等你唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:28.95,1:09:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:43.29,1:09:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:58.62,1:10:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换正面
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:50.95,1:11:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好性感
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:51.62,1:14:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:07.62,1:20:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:48.62,1:20:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太爽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:17.12,1:21:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:24.79,1:21:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:51.08,1:25:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:55.25,1:25:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:59.08,1:26:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:12.91,1:53:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:17.41,1:53:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得怎样都好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:24.41,1:53:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:28.75,1:53:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明什么都没想\N又好像想了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:36.91,1:53:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么感觉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:40.41,1:53:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渗透全身的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:15.91,1:55:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安\N早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:34.75,1:55:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了？\N没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:00.58,1:56:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:05.25,1:56:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现自己没有诚实面对\N自己的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:13.08,1:56:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是黑色好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:17.75,1:56:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色的内衣 黑色的车
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:24.41,1:56:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房间的壁纸也要换成黑色的
